items.description: New Layout - We've reorganized our features into three new modules: Asset, Supply Chain, and Production.  With this new layout, all of your favorite features are now organized in a more intuitive and user-friendly design.
Tooling Audit - Our Tooling Distribution, Utilization, and Status features are now combined into one space to give you a comprehensive overview of your tooling.
Demand Compliance - With this new feature, you'll be able to track whether your products and parts are meeting the weekly demand and quickly identify any that are falling behind schedule.
Customize and manage Tooling table tab
Create and assign workorder based on an asset
Create and assign maintenance/reject rate/pick list to companies or individual users in List Management

Create and assign maintenance/reject rate/pick list to companies or individual users in List Management Create and assign maintenance/reject rate/pick list to companies or individual users in List Management Create and assign maintenance/reject rate/pick list to companies or individual users in List Management
Asset Cost Depreciation Models - Unit of production based depreciation - Straight line depreciation
Added Brand profile to Category menu
Created Multi-chart view for Tooling page
Added Version History link to footer
Simplified Machine Matching for Mobile App
Added Last Maintenance Date & Last Refurbishment Date to tooling details
